formatText.richText: % Plan Achieved (Total Earned VS WWP)
Total Earned Hours by Category
Prelim Earned Hours
Weekly IWPs Category (Excluding Area 900s)
Discipline Weekly Work Plan
% Earned & %Spent VS WWP

calculatedFields.name: % Earned
calculatedFields.expression:
ifelse( 
isNull(sum({iwp_earnedhours})) 
 OR isNull({Planned Hours}) 
 OR {Planned Hours}=0,
NULL,
sum({iwp_earnedhours})/{Planned Hours}
 )

calculatedFields.name: % Spent
calculatedFields.expression:
ifelse( 
isNull( {Spent Hours} ) 
 OR isNull( {Planned Hours} ) 
 OR {Planned Hours}=0,
NULL,
{Spent Hours}/{Planned Hours}
 )

calculatedFields.name: %L3 Planned
calculatedFields.expression:
ifelse( isNull({Planned Hours}) OR isNull({L3 Required}) OR {L3 Required}=0,
NULL,{Planned Hours}/{L3 Required})

calculatedFields.name: L3 Achieved %
calculatedFields.expression:
ifelse( isNull({Earned Hours}) OR isNull({L3 Required}) OR {L3 Required}=0,
NULL,{Earned Hours}/{L3 Required})

calculatedFields.name: Preliminary PF

NULL,
{Earned Hours}/{Planned Hours}
 )
